(903, 'u_uruns', 'description', 132, 'en', 'Newcity Surface Cleaner ensures that frequently contacted surfaces in homes and workplaces are hygienic and fresh.\nIt has been developed to be cleaned properly. Effectively removes daily dirt, dust and stains\nIt does not leave residue on surfaces when cleaning.\nThanks to its formula that is compatible with different surface types, it can be used on tables, counters, cabinets, doors and etc.\nIt can be used safely in areas. Its pleasant scent creates a feeling of freshness after cleaning, while its practical\nIt facilitates daily cleaning routines with its use.\nIn addition to domestic use, it also provides an ideal solution for office, store and common area cleaning.', '2026-03-16 11:58:44', '2026-03-16 11:58:44'),
